{"tid":1042112,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"政府研究實踐擠塞徵費 冀管理車流令交通更暢順","createTime":"2019-03-01T10:28:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-05T00:39:19.000Z","uid":232278,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"a6936e3b3ce52cd11e4f8e67a857f7165b51ab2a","tid":1042112,"uid":232278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:28:28.000Z","msg":"擠塞徵費係<strong>源頭減車</strong>嘅第一步<br />\n太多私家車霸住條路 起幾多新路都無用<br />\n一架巴士平均載客比一架私家車多50倍<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">有乜理由比少數人佔用多數路面？</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sCvRIEd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FsCvRIEd.gif&h=2c3281a9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n要令更多私家車司機轉搭公共交通，先能夠根治塞車問題<br />\n就算三隧分流唔過，擠塞徵費都刻不容緩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n政府交代三隧分流調整方案，並計劃本月27日向立法會提出議案。運輸及房屋局局長陳帆表示，除了三隧分流方案外，政府亦將推出中環和鄰近地區電子道路收費的先導計劃，透過配置車內感應器，讓駕駛者免停車繳付隧道費，以及研究實踐擠塞徵費。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆說，擠塞徵費的理念是讓載客效率高，例如專營巴士享有較優惠的收費；而載客量較低的車輛類別，例如私家車，需要繳付較高費用。當局亦考慮引入不同時段、不同收費。<br />\n<br />\n陳帆強調，當局仔細研究擠塞徵費，目的並非為了收錢，而是透過徵費，在不同地區、不同時段，採取不同收費去管理車流，令交通更暢順。當局有詳細建議時，會向立法會及公眾交代。<br />\n<br />\n他說，運輸署將會展開擠塞徵費的研究，對所有政府收費隧道及道路的收費水平，作通盤考慮，包括將來可能歸屬政府的西隧及大欖隧道。政府在西隧專營權完結前，會完成檢討及諮詢工作，並草擬法例修定，以落實一套新收費水平建議，供立法會審議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1445500-20190301.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1445500-20190301.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=u7xsq8u58TeopDPyjGw7CxTmJET03dBbukdTSFliYCA%3D&h=7f2d1422\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1445500-20190301.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=bd189cd3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1445500-20190301.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"67f2bcc610abf44ac4c2f498d2b8cf5b935f0785","tid":1042112,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"希望中國公南直接駛入香港😂😂👍"},{"pid":"fad0e78c77de34d3571c2de34ddc77a27a4da8a4","tid":1042112,"uid":232278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"67f2bcc610abf44ac4c2f498d2b8cf5b935f0785","tid":1042112,"uid":198583,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:29:37.000Z","msg":"希望中國公南直接駛入香港😂😂👍"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-01T10:50:15.000Z","msg":"關咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ffcfce6a47f99847933348fd308c418d72ad25f9","tid":1042112,"uid":232278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-02T12:56:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d502864f6bb1f77808b022bf52600cae2549d769","tid":1042112,"uid":232278,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T23:04:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb073267a71cbb59332e4f2d3478887a421c7b65","tid":1042112,"uid":52942,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T23:09:20.000Z","msg":"返放工時間炒車罰返一百幾十萬就差唔多"},{"pid":"19a883cc8ad7676615e409709b215a0775a03dcb","tid":1042112,"uid":223385,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T23:18:52.000Z","msg":"警察响放工時段，夠胆抄L晒大道中D車先講啦"},{"pid":"6452084ad76c3d911b42dcef1197c39b15cb283d","tid":1042112,"uid":84081,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T23:22:27.000Z","msg":"多數渣車都係管理層<br />\n人工高根本唔怕Levy<br />\n<br />\n到時候啲搵食客貨車就慘"},{"pid":"364863fc445b06ef982d029aebf692c4d0d361b8","tid":1042112,"uid":44171,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"re